v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua m\u1ee9c 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3813\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3813\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3813 size-full\" title=\"c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i Fantasy\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-fantasy-1.jpg\" alt=\"T\u1ed5ng quan Fantasy\" width=\"800\" height=\"484\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-fantasy-1.jpg?v=1735821599 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-fantasy-1-300x182.jpg?v=1735821599 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-fantasy-1-768x465.jpg?v=1735821599 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3813\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">T\u1ed5ng quan Fantasy<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cach_choi_Fantasy\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i Fantasy<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 <\/span><b>c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i Fantasy<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3, b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u00f4ng tin, n\u1ed9i dung li\u00ean quan l\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Doi_hinh_so_do_Fantasy\"><\/span><b>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 Fantasy<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sau khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n, s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p \u0111\u0103ng nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i. Trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh g\u1ed3m c\u00f3 15 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, m\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ecdn ra t\u1ed1i \u0111a 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh khi ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea5u theo <strong>c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i Fantasy<\/strong> c\u00f3 11 ng\u01b0\u1eddi tham gia \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian di\u1ec5n ra gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ed7i v\u00f2ng l\u00e0 1 l\u1ea7n mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ea1n b\u1ecb tr\u1eeb \u0111i 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0o t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 trong v\u00f2ng \u0111\u00f3.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3814\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3814\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3814 size-full\" title=\"c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i Fantasy\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-fantasy-2.jpg\" alt=\"C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i Fantasy\" width=\"800\" height=\"457\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-fantasy-2.jpg?v=1735821601 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-fantasy-2-300x171.jpg?v=1735821601 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-fantasy-2-768x439.jpg?v=1735821601 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3814\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i Fantasy<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tinh_diem_trong_tran_dau\"><\/span><b>T\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec3m trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Theo <\/span><b>c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i Fantasy<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 b\u1ea1n nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 l\u00e0 t\u00ednh d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean 11 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t ra s\u00e2n. Tuy nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t hay nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n ch\u1ecdn kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i trong tu\u1ea7n th\u00ec s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho anh em. B\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f9y \u00fd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3, mi\u1ec5n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o c\u00f3 1 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n v\u00e0 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7, 1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u01a1i kho\u1ea3ng \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 60 ph\u00fat: 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u01a1i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n 60 ph\u00fat, kh\u00f4ng t\u00ednh th\u1eddi gian b\u00f9 gi\u1edd: 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 ghi b\u00e0n: 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng: 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng: 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed: 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 gi\u1eef l\u01b0\u1edbi an to\u00e0n: 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi: 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 \u0111\u1ee7 3 l\u1ea7n l\u00e0: 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 penalty: 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0Tr\u01b0\u1ee3t penalty: -2 \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 2 band thua: -1 \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng: -1 \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf: -3 \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0: -2 \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110i\u1ec3m th\u01b0\u1edfng: t\u1eeb 1 \u0111\u1ebfn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3815\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3815\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3815 size-full\" title=\"c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i Fantasy\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-fantasy-3.jpg\" alt=\"T\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec3m trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-fantasy-3.jpg?v=1735821602 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-fantasy-3-300x188.jpg?v=1735821602 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-fantasy-3-768x480.jpg?v=1735821602 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3815\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">T\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec3m trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Chuyen_nhuong_cau_thu\"><\/span><b>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u <\/span><b>c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i Fantasy<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, anh em c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c trong chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 trong tay kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh ch\u1ecdn mua 15 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec1u, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch chi ti\u00eau h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, th\u00f4ng minh. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 ai c\u0169ng s\u1ebd mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, nh\u01b0ng \u0111i k\u00e8m th\u00ec gi\u00e1 cao.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sau khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7, b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n mua b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n, chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u l\u1ef1c cho t\u1edbi khi h\u1ea1n ch\u00f3t c\u1ee7a v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c di\u1ec5n ra. Sau \u0111\u00f3, anh em \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng duy nh\u1ea5t 1 l\u1ea7n trong m\u1ed7i v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u. Mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ti\u1ebfp th\u00ec b\u1ecb tr\u1eeb 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0o t\u1ed5ng.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">V\u1ec1 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, n\u00f3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i li\u00ean t\u1ee5c trong su\u1ed1t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o c\u00e1c bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. N\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 n\u00e2ng l\u00ean trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra th\u00ec khi b\u00e1n ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u1ea3n l\u1eddi.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3816\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3816\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3816 size-full\" title=\"c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i Fantasy\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-fantasy-4.jpg\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7\" width=\"800\" height=\"457\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-fantasy-4.jpg?v=1735821603 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-fantasy-4-300x171.jpg?v=1735821603 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-fantasy-4-768x439.jpg?v=1735821603 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3816\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Mot_so_tinh_nang_tro_giup\"><\/span><b>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u00ednh n\u0103ng tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Khi tham gia <\/span><b>c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i Fantasy<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, anh em nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 quy\u1ec1n tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 d\u00f9ng 1 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf 1 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Bench Boost: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cho ph\u00e9p ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i c\u1ed9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a 15 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n 11 ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Free Hit:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Thay \u0111\u1ed5i h\u1ebft nh\u1eefng c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 trong 1 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Triple Captain: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cho ph\u00e9p \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u00e2n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, thay v\u00ec nh\u00e2n 2 nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Wildcard: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong \u0111\u1ed9i, d\u00f9ng 2 l\u1ea7n trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Loi_ket\"><\/span><b>L\u1eddi k\u1ebft<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 n\u1ed9i dung v\u1ec1 <\/span><b>c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i Fantasy<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> m\u00e0 SV368 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n. Hy v\u1ecdng qua \u0111\u00f3, anh em bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u th\u00f4ng tin chi ti\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham gia ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i Fantasy lu\u00f4n nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi. \u0110